reviewText: A lot of great Saturday morning classics from the past.  Brings back so many great memories.  Thank you.
Great memories of my childhood in the 1950s.  I can't believe how primitive television was as compared to today. Howdy!

I grew up in the 50's and looked forward to getting the DVD as soon as I knew about the DVD.  Amazon was 1st on the internet list, and have bought from Amazon before, so didn't even hesitate to get this wonderful DVD.
